{"tid":473003,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"2017高中視覺藝術科心得分享","createTime":"2017-11-18T18:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T18:08:51.000Z","uid":65788,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bdd379032d1bb20994b75573e8bfa4f7cdbf63f2","tid":473003,"uid":65788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T18:08:51.000Z","msg":"2017 va dse拎左5**，之後返學校教va，發現好多同學仔都係唔識做sba<br />\n<br />\n知道好多同學仔都準備交S BA，所以有感而發想講少少。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/015826_5161f0721210a872d2acf0b799e67e11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F015826_5161f0721210a872d2acf0b799e67e11.jpg&h=06b8a7c1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/015828_eb39f05a41487793832242c0940e1657.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F015828_eb39f05a41487793832242c0940e1657.jpg&h=62ea7b78&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/015831_2c9792f457f614a8dc7c06a7257dd3de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F015831_2c9792f457f614a8dc7c06a7257dd3de.jpg&h=7065e580&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/015835_fd2144a3fb2b6afcb22801d225b40f94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F015835_fd2144a3fb2b6afcb22801d225b40f94.jpg&h=9803ec62&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/015838_cd0cee9372dd89f420d43882e6609044.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F015838_cd0cee9372dd89f420d43882e6609044.jpg&h=edfe6917&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上係我S BA嘅規模，其實做到咁上下，你老師一定會比高，因為佢地都要交成績見人，佢地比分就等於你公開試成績。<br />\n<br />\n作品媒介要不同，唔好做得咁純藝術，最好多細緻位。<br />\n<br />\n研究工作簿千祈唔好離題！多啲用藝術用語，因為你係做緊藝術研究，唔係日記簿。<br />\n<br />\n藝術家做藝術品當然可以唔詳盡解釋，例如佢㗎意念，佢使用呢個媒介嘅原因。但作為一份考試作品，你根本冇得唔詳盡解釋。解釋嘅方法簡單啲講，就係用晒啲意念引發、藝術家評賞、媒介試驗等等佢解釋你作品嘅由來，好多同學就係做唔到呢一點！<br />\n<br />\n其實仲有好多野講，更加想知你地有啲咩問題出現，不妨可以問吓我。<br />\n<br />\ntg: vt9787"}]}